summary: no offense but the captain underpants movie did the transition from cartoon to more 3D style animation the best almost...

summary: So I picked up detective pikachu since the movie is coming out, and I realized pikachu's voice is rather familiar so I did so...
body:
So I picked up detective pikachu since the movie is coming out, and I realized pikachu’s voice is rather familiar so I did so Internet searching and he’s voiced by Kaiji Tang. I then realized why the voice is so familiar, it’s because Kaiji Tang also voices Owain/Odin from the fire emblem series.

Now all I can picture is Owain/Odin making pikachu noises.
